@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qswxth(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.56 - tmp + 0.34)) / ((tmp + 0.49 + v2 + 0.13) / (v1 + 0.61 + v1 + 0.26)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
